reviewText: The World of Sid and Marty Krofft: Collector's Edition Volume 6. This volume was part of the Columbia House release of 10 volumes. In this volume on HR Pufnstuf: The Golden Key, Lidsville: Fly Now, Vacuum Later, Electra Woman and Dyna Girl: Empress of Evil part 1, Sigmund and the Sea Monsters: The Nasty Nephew, The Lost Saucer: My Fair Robot, and Electra Woman and Dyna Girl: Empress of Evil part 2.
